fs.fibu2.data.format
Class JournalExportLoader

java.lang.Object
  fs.fibu2.data.format.JournalExportLoader

public class JournalExportLoader
extends java.lang.Object

This class provides access to JournalExports via their ID. It also provides methods to add a .class file of a JournalExport.
